data.description:
Back on the market! No fault of the Sellers as Buyer's were unable to sell their home in time to buy. 

Seller is motivated.  

Looking for a great home in Elizabethton, Tennessee? Look no further! This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom 2,318 square foot two story home has it all. 

When you walk in the door you will be welcomed by a cozy living room with a fireplace. The main level features two bedrooms, a bathroom, a formal dining room, kitchen and a laundry room! 

The upstairs has 2 bedrooms, an office and a full bathroom. The full basement offers plenty of storage space and includes pool table and weight lifting equipment - perfect for any fitness enthusiast. 

 Enjoy your afternoons on the covered front porch or relax in the privacy of your backyard that is fenced off from neighbors. 

Plus, there's an additional bonus of having a detached two car garage!

 Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own this wonderful family home - schedule your showing today!
